| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-3049 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9ac9bae9-344f-57cb-a9bf-5feddcc9efd9"
